{"履修期": "春学期", "主な教授言語": "英語", "授業目的": "本授業では、社会学を「英語で」学ぶことを通して、英語能力と社会学的知識の双方を高める。", "到達目標": "受講者が英語で社会学を学ぶ上で必要とされる以下の能力を身につけることを、到達目標とする。・英語で社会学部を学ぶ能力。・社会学の基礎を理解する能力。・英語でプレゼンテーションする能力。・英語ペーパーを書く能力。", "特記事項": "【合併】Sociology in English Ａ　２（社会学部）/Sociology in English Ａ　２（社会学部）", "関連科目": "", "授業の概要・背景": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;margin:0mm;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:游明朝,serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:-webkit-standard,serif;font-size:10pt;background-image:none;background-position:0% 0%;background-size:auto;background-repeat:repeat;background-attachment:scroll;background-origin:padding-box;background-clip:border-box;\">Students who take the course are expected to have interests in socio-political issues and phenomena in contemporary societies as well as active access to a variety of media programs taking up these topics (e.g. television news programs, newspaper articles, posts on SNS, etc.)<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:-webkit-standard,serif;font-size:10pt;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;background-image:none;background-position:0% 0%;background-size:auto;background-repeat:repeat;background-attachment:scroll;background-origin:padding-box;background-clip:border-box;\"><span style=\"text-align:start;\">受講生には「英語で社会学する」ことに日頃から関心を抱き、現代社会における社会事象・現象を「英語で」伝えるさまざまな媒体（テレビニュース、新聞記事、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:-webkit-standard,serif;font-size:10pt;background-image:none;background-position:0% 0%;background-size:auto;background-repeat:repeat;background-attachment:scroll;background-origin:padding-box;background-clip:border-box;\">SNS</span><span style=\"font-size:10pt;background-image:none;background-position:0% 0%;background-size:auto;background-repeat:repeat;background-attachment:scroll;background-origin:padding-box;background-clip:border-box;\">投稿、等）に積極的にアクセスすることが求められる。</span></span></p>", "授業方法": "Two lecturers conduct the course.二名の講師が授業担当するオムニバス形式の授業。", "トピック": {"第1回": ["<span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">【スタートアップウィーク】</span><span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">オンライン授業（オンデマンド型）</span><span style=\"font-size:13.28px;\">《90分》</span><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;margin:0mm;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:游明朝,serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:-webkit-standard,serif;font-size:10pt;background-image:none;background-position:0% 0%;background-size:auto;background-repeat:repeat;background-attachment:scroll;background-origin:padding-box;background-clip:border-box;\">Introduction: Introducing the purpose of Sociology in English and explaining how the course will be conducted.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;margin:0mm;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:游明朝,serif;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:-webkit-standard,serif;font-size:10pt;background-image:none;background-position:0% 0%;background-size:auto;background-repeat:repeat;background-attachment:scroll;background-origin:padding-box;background-clip:border-box;\"><a href=\"https://kwanseio365-my.sharepoint.com/:v:/g/personal/fjh81546_nuc_kwansei_ac_jp/IQCt2ocuTd45TZLRTzNd7X8PATHyXR24JaSSaiIYZMVVdr8?nav=eyJyZWZlcnJhbEluZm8iOnsicmVmZXJyYWxBcHAiOiJPbmVEcml2ZUZvckJ1c2luZXNzIiwicmVmZXJyYWxBcHBQbGF0Zm9ybSI6IldlYiIsInJlZmVycmFsTW9kZSI6InZpZXciLCJyZWZlcnJhbFZpZXciOiJNeUZpbGVzTGlua0NvcHkifX0&amp;e=YERNzF\">SIE Introduction Video_on demand.mp4</a></span></p></div>", "Watching the video and understanding the basic policy of the course."], "第2回": ["<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;margin:0mm;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:游明朝,serif;\"><span style=\"font-size:10pt;background-image:none;background-position:0% 0%;background-size:auto;background-repeat:repeat;background-attachment:scroll;background-origin:padding-box;background-clip:border-box;\">【コアウィークス</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:-webkit-standard,serif;font-size:10pt;background-image:none;background-position:0% 0%;back